node.text: Pro Pack feature ~ Cut out a section by double tapping a serpentine dot…then another. Then you can cut or copy a section out to then edit a better line or merge that section later into another trip/Route. Always duplicate your Collection before major editing (Note: this example is just for show and this is not a suggested line for the Baja 400…)

node.text: BITD Vegas to Reno ~ New video on the basics of race prepping a GPS file ~ You can go watch the full video on our website training page and I will put a link to it up in our stories ~ Sorry for the delay in getting it up on our channel but You Tube, for some reason, takes days to process a video. node.text: BITD Vegas to Reno ~ New video on the basics of race prepping a GPS file ~ You can go watch the full video on our website training page and I will put a link to it up in our stories ~ Sorry for the delay in getting it up on our channel but You Tube, for some reason, takes days to process a video. Where as we were able to get it up on @vimeo in just 30 minutes in 4K rez… ~ With the V2R coming this week we wanted to get it out ASAP…so to those subscribed to our @youtube channel..sorry for their delay 🤷‍♂️ ~ Get LEADNAV GPS in the Apple App Store 👈
